description:
David Spade (FATHER OF THE YEAR, A POLAROID GUY IN A SNAPCHAT WORLD) joins Unqualified this week! First, David delves into his childhood and bonds with Sim over a party they both attended where David earned the title of “lady’s man” in Sim’s eyes. Next, David and Anna role-play a date and David coaches Anna about how to attract men. Next, they talk stand-up, and David talks about his crazy experiences working with Rob Schneider and they play a round of deal breakers. After, they call Brittany, who doesn’t know how to tell her romantic interest that he smells bad, and Megan, who is conflicted about reconnecting with a guy that ghosted her. Sit back, relax and prepare to laugh!

Follow Us!

David Spade: @davidspade

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified
